OL,3,CFarmers call for inheritance tax U-
OL,4,Cturn ahead of crunch talks with
OL,5,Cministers
OL,7,FReversing plans to charge inheritance
OL,8,Ftax on farms is "the only sensible
OL,9,Fcourse of action", the head of the
OL,10,FNational Farmers' Union has said as he
OL,11,Fprepares for crunch talks with the
OL,12,FEnvironment Secretary.
OL,14,FNFU president Tom Bradshaw is to meet
OL,15,FSteve Reed on Monday amid a growing
OL,16,Ffurore over the Chancellor's decision
OL,17,Fto make farms subject to inheritance
OL,18,Ftax.
