OL,3,CFarmers call for inheritance tax U-
OL,4,Cturn ahead of crunch talks with
OL,5,Cministers
OL,7,FUnder plans announced at the Budget,
OL,8,Finheritance tax will be charged at 20%
OL,9,Fon farms worth more than #1 million,
OL,10,Falthough the Chancellor has said in
OL,11,Fsome cases the threshold could in
OL,12,Fpractice be around #3 million.
OL,14,FBut writing in the Daily Telegraph, Mr
OL,15,FBradshaw said the prospect of being
OL,16,Funable to pass their businesses on to
OL,17,Ftheir children would be "the final
OL,18,Fstraw" for many farmers.
