OL,4,Cturn ahead of crunch talks with
OL,5,Cministers
OL,7,FHe said: "The vast majority of the
OL,8,Fpeople who will bear the brunt of this
OL,9,Fdecision aren't wealthy people with
OL,10,Fhuge cash reserves hidden away.
OL,12,F"They are families that have often
OL,13,Fspent generations building up their
OL,14,Ffarm businesses to provide food for
OL,15,Fthe nation, often on very tight profit
OL,16,Fmargins.
