OL,5,Cministers
OL,7,F"Their businesses have struggled
OL,8,Fthrough all the changes caused by
OL,9,FBrexit, they've suffered years of
OL,10,Fbeing squeezed to the lowest margins
OL,11,Fimaginable, with costs of production
OL,12,Fskyrocketing, they've been battered by
OL,13,Fincreasingly extreme weather
OL,14,Fconditions. They have nothing left to
OL,15,Fgive."
