OL,7,FTax experts have suggested the changes
OL,8,Fcould affect fewer than 500 farms a
OL,9,Fyear, once the tax thresholds and
OL,10,Ffarmers giving their property to their
OL,11,Fchildren before they die are taken
OL,12,Finto account.
OL,14,FBut Mr Bradshaw said the Treasury had
OL,15,Fa "completely skewed view of the
OL,16,Fstructure of farming in the UK".
