OL,3,CFarmers call for inheritance tax U-
OL,4,Cturn ahead of crunch talks with
OL,5,Cministers
OL,7,FHe said: "Very few viable farms are
OL,8,Fworth under #1 million. That could buy
OL,9,Fyou 50 acres and a house today. No
OL,10,Fviable food-producing business is 50
OL,11,Facres. The average farm in the UK is
OL,12,Fmore than 250 acres.
OL,14,F"The only sensible course of action
OL,15,Ffor the future of family farms across
OL,16,Fthe country, as well as for the sake
OL,17,Fof Britain's food security and our
OL,18,Flegislated environmental targets, is
OL,19,Fto reverse this decision."
