OL,7,FChancellor Rachel Reeves told the
OL,8,FBBC's Sunday With Laura Kuenssberg:
OL,9,F"Only a very small number of
OL,10,Fagricultural properties will be
OL,11,Faffected, but last year the benefits
OL,12,Fof agricultural property relief, 40%
OL,13,Fof the benefit was felt by 7% of the
OL,14,Fwealthiest land owners.
OL,16,F"I don't think it is affordable to
OL,17,Fcarry on with a relief like that when
OL,18,Four public finances are under so much
OL,19,Fpressure."
